<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.2">
<l>malaipuraitōḷ maṉṉavarum māratarum maṟṟum</l>
<l>palarkulaiya nūṟṟuvarum paṭṭaḻiyap pārttaṉ</l>
<l>cilaivaḷaiyat tiṇṭērmēl muṉṉiṉṟa ceṅka</l>
<l>ṇalavalaivan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The red-eyed babbler who stood in the fore on a sturdy chariot</l>
<l>as Pārtha bent [his] bow so that the hundred perished</l>
<l>[and] so that the kings with shoulders that resemble mountains,</l>
<l>warriors on chariots, and many others were ruined and perished,</l>
<l>is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
